      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's an interesting distinction. You mentioned that Case B's background is seen as a \"risk factor.\" Can you expand on that? Specifically, why would living in an \"underserved urban neighborhood\" or having \"sporadic employment\" be considered an aggravating factor for a non-violent drug offense, compared to someone with a more stable background?",
